         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Extract current PSW                                                  00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   EPSW  &REG                    * Register set to be used        00200000
.*                                                                      00210000
.* &REG  specifies an even register. The PSW will be placed in register 00220000
.*       &REG and &REG+1.                                               00230000
.*                                                                      00240000
.********************************************************************** 00241001
.*                                                                      00242001
.*       IMPORTANT NOTICE                                               00243001
.*       ========= ======                                               00244001
.*                                                                      00245001
